Introduction

This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

iDev - Innovation Development.

Base URL

https://estater.biz

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

Queues

API для работы с очередями

List of queues

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queues"
);

const params = {
    "page": "16",
    "sort": "neque",
    "status": "12",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/queues',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'page'=> '16',
            'sort'=> 'neque',
            'status'=> '12',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queues?page=16&sort=neque&status=12" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "message": "Unauthenticated."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

GET api/v1/queues

Query Parameters

page  integer optional  

Номер страницы с результатами выдачи

sort  string optional  

Поле для сортировки. По-умолчанию 'id|desc'

status  integer optional  

Статус очереди

Create queue

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "dolorem",
    "status": 8,
    "is_cron": 7,
    "slot_duration": 8,
    "mon": "laborum",
    "tue": "veniam",
    "wed": "omnis",
    "thu": "dolores",
    "fri": "beatae",
    "sat": "ut",
    "sun": "incidunt",
    "break": "est",
    "service_id": [
        19
    ]
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'name' => 'dolorem',
            'status' => 8,
            'is_cron' => 7,
            'slot_duration' => 8,
            'mon' => 'laborum',
            'tue' => 'veniam',
            'wed' => 'omnis',
            'thu' => 'dolores',
            'fri' => 'beatae',
            'sat' => 'ut',
            'sun' => 'incidunt',
            'break' => 'est',
            'service_id' => [
                19,
            ],
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request POST \
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"dolorem\",
    \"status\": 8,
    \"is_cron\": 7,
    \"slot_duration\": 8,
    \"mon\": \"laborum\",
    \"tue\": \"veniam\",
    \"wed\": \"omnis\",
    \"thu\": \"dolores\",
    \"fri\": \"beatae\",
    \"sat\": \"ut\",
    \"sun\": \"incidunt\",
    \"break\": \"est\",
    \"service_id\": [
        19
    ]
}"
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

POST api/v1/queue

Body Parameters

name  string  

Название очереди

status  integer optional  

optional Статус очереди (1 - активная, 0 - не активная)

is_cron  integer optional  

optional Название очереди

slot_duration  integer optional  

optional Длительность слота, мин

mon  string optional  

optional Время работы в понедельник (08:00-17:00)

tue  string optional  

optional Время работы во вторник

wed  string optional  

optional Время работы в среду

thu  string optional  

optional Время работы в четверг

fri  string optional  

optional Время работы в пятницу

sat  string optional  

optional Время работы в субботу

sun  string optional  

optional Время работы в воскресенье

break  string optional  

optional Время перерыва (12:00-13:00)

service_id  integer[] optional  

optional Массив IDs сервисов

    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',

        ],
    ]

$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Update queue

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue/15"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "rem",
    "status": 10,
    "is_cron": 15,
    "slot_duration": 16,
    "mon": "aut",
    "tue": "commodi",
    "wed": "quis",
    "thu": "nostrum",
    "fri": "voluptas",
    "sat": "sunt",
    "sun": "labore",
    "break": "quo",
    "service_id": [
        1
    ]
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "PUT",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->put(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue/15',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'name' => 'rem',
            'status' => 10,
            'is_cron' => 15,
            'slot_duration' => 16,
            'mon' => 'aut',
            'tue' => 'commodi',
            'wed' => 'quis',
            'thu' => 'nostrum',
            'fri' => 'voluptas',
            'sat' => 'sunt',
            'sun' => 'labore',
            'break' => 'quo',
            'service_id' => [
                1,
            ],
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request PUT \
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue/15" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"rem\",
    \"status\": 10,
    \"is_cron\": 15,
    \"slot_duration\": 16,
    \"mon\": \"aut\",
    \"tue\": \"commodi\",
    \"wed\": \"quis\",
    \"thu\": \"nostrum\",
    \"fri\": \"voluptas\",
    \"sat\": \"sunt\",
    \"sun\": \"labore\",
    \"break\": \"quo\",
    \"service_id\": [
        1
    ]
}"
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Delete specified queue

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue/20"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "DELETE",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->delete(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue/20',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request DELETE \
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/queue/20" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"

Category of Laws

API для работы с категориями законов.

List of law category

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/law_categories"
);

const params = {
    "page": "1",
    "sort": "dolor",
    "search": "voluptatem",
    "status": "deleniti",
    "lang": "doloribus",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "status": "visible",
    "lang": "uk"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/law_categories',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'page'=> '1',
            'sort'=> 'dolor',
            'search'=> 'voluptatem',
            'status'=> 'deleniti',
            'lang'=> 'doloribus',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 'visible',
            'lang' => 'uk',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/law_categories?page=1&sort=dolor&search=voluptatem&status=deleniti&lang=doloribus" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"status\": \"visible\",
    \"lang\": \"uk\"
}"

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "message": "Unauthenticated."
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

GET api/v1/law_categories

Query Parameters

page  integer optional  

Номер страницы с результатами выдачи

sort  string optional  

Поле для сортировки. По-умолчанию 'id|desc'

search  string optional  

Строка, которая должна содержаться в результатах выдачи

status  string optional  

Статус отображения (возможные значения visible, hidden)

lang  string optional  

На каком языке возвращать результаты (возможные значения uk, en)

Body Parameters

status  string optional  

Must be one of visible or hidden.

lang  string optional  

Must be one of uk or en.

Create law category

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/law_category"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",

    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/category/16"
);

    "page": "1",
    "status": "hidden",
    "lang": "excepturi",
};

    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/category/16',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'page'=> '1',
            'status'=> 'hidden',
            'lang'=> 'excepturi',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/category/16?page=1&status=hidden&lang=excepturi" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"

    "user_id": "temporibus",

    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    "status": "active"
};

    method: "GET",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/entries',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'page'=> 'dignissimos',
            'sort'=> 'impedit',
            'search'=> 'omnis',
            'service_id'=> 'harum',
            'user_id'=> 'temporibus',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 'active',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/entries?page=dignissimos&sort=impedit&search=omnis&service_id=harum&user_id=temporibus" \

Example request:

        "quidem"
    ]
};

    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/entry',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 'et',
            'user_id' => 'inventore',
            'service_id' => 'non',
            'text' => 'neque',
            'phone' => 'ut',
            'file' => [
                'quidem',
            ],
        ],
    ]
);

    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/entry" \

    \"user_id\": \"inventore\",

Request      

GET api/v1/reports

Query Parameters

page  integer optional  

Номер страницы с результатами выдачи

sort  string optional  

Поле для сортировки. По-умолчанию 'id|desc'

search  string optional  

Строка, которая должна содержаться в результатах выдачи

status  string optional  

Статус отображения (возможные значения visible, hidden)

lang  string optional  

На каком языке возвращать результаты (возможные значения uk, en)

full  boolean optional  

Получение списка без пагинации

Body Parameters

status  string optional  

Must be one of visible or hidden.

Create report

requires authentication

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/report"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    "status": 1,
    "year": 3,
    "month": 14,
    "file": "at"
};

    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->post(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/report',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 1,
            'year' => 3,
            'month' => 14,
            'file' => 'at',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/reports"
);

const params = {
    "page": "7",
    "sort": "ut",
    "search": "esse",
    "status": "sit",
    "lang": "ut",
    "full": "0",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "status": "hidden"
};

    method: "GET",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/reports',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'page'=> '7',
            'sort'=> 'ut',
            'search'=> 'esse',
            'status'=> 'sit',
            'lang'=> 'ut',
            'full'=> '0',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 'hidden',
        ],
    ]
);

На каком языке возвращать результаты (возможные значения uk, en)

Получение списка без пагинации

Body Parameters

Must be one of visible or hidden.

Get specified report

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/report/13"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "status": "hidden"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/report/13',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'status' => 'hidden',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/report/13" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"status\": \"hidden\"
}"

    "sort": "porro",
    "search": "aut",
    "user_id": "10",
};

    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/roles',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'page'=> '10',
            'sort'=> 'porro',
            'search'=> 'aut',
            'user_id'=> '10',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/roles?page=10&sort=porro&search=aut&user_id=10" \

Search

API для глобального поиска.

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/search"
);

const params = {
    "q": "sit",
    "lang": "accusantium",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "q": "m",
    "lang": "en"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/search',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'q'=> 'sit',
            'lang'=> 'accusantium',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'q' => 'm',
            'lang' => 'en',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/search?q=sit&lang=accusantium" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"q\": \"m\",
    \"lang\": \"en\"
}"

Get specified tag

Example request:
const url = new URL(
    "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/tag/4"
);

const params = {
    "lang": "fuga",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "lang": "en"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
$client = new \GuzzleHttp\Client();
$response = $client->get(
    'https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/tag/4',
    [
        'headers' => [
            'Content-Type' => 'application/json',
            'Accept' => 'application/json',
        ],
        'query' => [
            'lang'=> 'fuga',
        ],
        'json' => [
            'lang' => 'en',
        ],
    ]
);
$body = $response->getBody();
print_r(json_decode((string) $body));
curl --request GET \
    --get "https://estater.biz/api/v1/web/tag/4?lang=fuga" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"lang\": \"en\"
}"
